snippet.title: YIIK I.V Trailer No.1
snippet.description:
YIIK I.V (Intravenous) is a free update to YIIK: A Postmodern RPG releasing in 2022.
www.yiikrpg.com
Analogue Girl Digital Buttons available on Bandcamp and Spotify! 
Lyrics:
Analogue Girl
With Digital Buttons
Analogue Girl
With a plastic shell
Analogue Girl
With silicone graphics
So real you could have ‘em
So real you can’t doubt ‘em
Simulated 
Simulated 
with havok 
Come to purgatory with me
Run from purgatory for me
Come to purgatory with me
Run from purgatory for me
(Scream)
Digital girl with analogue feelings
Human girl in a plastic shell
I’d follow
I’d follow 
You to havoc.

Music performed by Sam Stilwell
Music and Lyrics by Andrew Allanson

https://andrewallanson.bandcamp.com/track/analogue-girl-digital-buttons

https://open.spotify.com/album/6witiaF0zDEKqfTISfcYH6?si=Tpf36moBRS6A7-doQsrimg
